---

<section id="reviews" class="py-10 md:py-16 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- 輕微背景裝飾 -->
    <div
        class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-20 -mr-20 w-80 h-80 bg-blue-50 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-60 pointer-events-none"
    >
    </div>
    <div
        class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -mb-20 -ml-20 w-72 h-72 bg-orange-50 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-60 pointer-events-none"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl relative z-10">
        <!-- 標題區塊 (已移除總評分) -->
        <div class="text-center mb-8">
            <span
                class="text-primary font-bold tracking-widest text-sm uppercase mb-2 block"
                >Reviews</span
            >
            <h2
                class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-heading leading-tight"
            >
                病患好評
            </h2>
            <p
                class="text-gray-500 mt-4 text-sm md:text-base max-w-2xl mx-auto"
            >
                感謝每一位患者的信任與真實回饋，您的健康是我們最大的目標。
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- 卡片與左右按鈕區塊 -->
